## Error Groups:

1. **`children` prop missing from `FC` types** (~60+ errors) - React 18 `FC` no longer includes `children` implicitly. Many custom components need `PropsWithChildren` or explicit `children` prop.
2. **`@patternfly/react-charts` cannot find module** (~20 errors) - Import path changed in PF6.
3. **`FormGroupHelperText` doesn't accept `children`** (~40+ errors) - API changed in PF6.
4. **`MenuToggleProps` doesn't have `placeholder`** (~25+ errors) - API changed, now `isPlaceholder` or different approach.
5. **`ExternalLink` doesn't accept `children`** (~7 errors) - Custom component needs fix.
6. **`ExpandSection` doesn't accept `children`/`toggleText`** (~12 errors) - Custom component needs fix.
7. **`DragDrop`/`Draggable`/`Droppable` removed from PF core** (3 errors) - Moved to `@patternfly/react-drag-drop`.
8. **`SearchItem` doesn't accept `children`** (~44 errors) - Custom component needs fix.
9. **Various custom components missing `children` prop** - SidebarEditorProvider, StateHandler, PendingChangesAlert, SectionListItem, etc.
10. **`@patternfly/quickstarts` and `react-log-viewer` webpack module resolution errors** (5 errors)
11. **Miscellaneous type errors** - fromNow return type, RowProps missing index, ToolbarFilter children, etc.

